description: Deletes the publishing definition with the specified destinationId.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the detector associated with the publishing destination to delete. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: DestinationId
parameters.description: The ID of the publishing destination to delete.
